entity.name: Updates on the Covid-19 situation in the Philippines
entity.description: This page provides real-time updates on the Covid-19 situation from trusted and official sources.

text:
BREAKING: Number of recoveries from COVID-19 in the Philippines reaches 353, surpassing number of deaths. Coronavirus cases in the country rise to 5,453, the Health Department reports.

Follow our live blog for more updates: https://t.co/S6VLGJnPcx https://t.co/eqMfyLbCqN
